          "audioFile": "wraith_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo03_01",
          "audioUrl": "audio/wraith_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo03_01.mp3",
          "text": "Glad you're on our side Drifter",
          "duration": 1.714
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "character": "Drifter",
          "audioFile": "drifter_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo03_02",
          "audioUrl": "audio/drifter_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo03_02.mp3",
          "text": "You should be Wraith, otherwise I-",
          "duration": 2.86
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "character": "Wraith",
          "audioFile": "wraith_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo03_03",
          "audioUrl": "audio/wraith_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo03_03.mp3",
          "text": "No need to threaten me, I'm already scared of you.",
          "duration": 2.961
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "character": "Drifter",
          "audioFile": "drifter_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo03_04",
          "audioUrl": "audio/drifter_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo03_04.mp3",
          "text": "Very good.",
          "duration": 2.571
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "conversationId": "dynamo_mcginnis_convo01",
      "lines": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "character": "Mcginnis",
          "audioFile": "forge_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo01_01",
          "audioUrl": "audio/forge_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo01_01.mp3",
          "text": "How's that body working out for you?",
          "duration": 1.735
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "character": "Dynamo",
          "audioFile": "dynamo_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo01_02",
          "audioUrl": "audio/dynamo_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo01_02.mp3",
          "text": "Splendid all things considered.",
          "duration": 1.894
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "character": "Mcginnis",
          "audioFile": "forge_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo01_03",
          "audioUrl": "audio/forge_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo01_03.mp3",
          "text": "Well, if you ever want an upgrade or something give me a call.",
          "duration": 3.069
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "character": "Dynamo",
          "audioFile": "dynamo_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo01_04",
          "audioUrl": "audio/dynamo_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo01_04.mp3",
          "text": "I appreciate the offer Ms McGinnis, but hopefully after today your services won't be needed.",
          "duration": 4.577
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "conversationId": "dynamo_mcginnis_convo02",
      "lines": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "character": "Dynamo",
          "audioFile": "dynamo_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo02_01",
          "audioUrl": "audio/dynamo_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo02_01.mp3",
          "text": "Have you ever considered being an adjunct professor?",
          "duration": 2.303
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "character": "Mcginnis",
          "audioFile": "forge_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo02_02",
          "audioUrl": "audio/forge_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo02_02.mp3",
          "text": "No, I'd make a really bad teacher.",
          "duration": 2.219
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "character": "Dynamo",
          "audioFile": "dynamo_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo02_03",
          "audioUrl": "audio/dynamo_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo02_03.mp3",
          "text": "Why do you think that?",
          "duration": 1.066
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "character": "Mcginnis",
          "audioFile": "forge_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo02_04",
          "audioUrl": "audio/forge_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo02_04.mp3",
          "text": "I don't know how I do what I do, it just comes naturally\u2026 if I tried to teach someone it would probably boil down to me saying \"try it again, but don't suck this time\"",
          "duration": 8.494
        },
        {
          "order": 5,
          "character": "Dynamo",
          "audioFile": "dynamo_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo02_05",
          "audioUrl": "audio/dynamo_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo02_05.mp3",
          "text": "Good god, you'd be the Lash of acadameia.",
          "duration": 2.52
        },
        {
          "order": 6,
          "character": "Mcginnis",
          "audioFile": "forge_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo02_06",
          "audioUrl": "audio/forge_match_start_dynamo_forge_convo02_06.mp3",
          "text": "You say it like that, I kind of wanna give it a try.",
          "duration": 2.349
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}